-- Aeromexico Says Aimia Seeks Stake in Its Loyalty Unit
-- B y   C r a y t o n   H a r r i s o n
-- 2012-08-09T22:47:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-09/aeromexico-says-aimia-seeks-stake-in-its-loyalty-unit-correct-.html
(Corrects name of the company in first paragraph.)  Grupo Aeromexico SAB is in talks with
Aimia Inc., which is seeking to increase its stake in the
airline’s loyalty unit.  The parties seek to reach an agreement on Premier Loyalty &
Marketing SAPI, which operates Aeromexico’s Club Premier
program, by the end of 2012, the airline said today in a
statement distributed by PR Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Crayton Harrison in Mexico City at 
